      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoIs used in validation (NIH, shear stress distribution, relative hemolysis index RH) are directly relevant to the COU decision metric.",
      "rationale": "Validation QoIs (NIH, volume-averaged scalar shear stress, RH) are identical to the COU decision metrics. No surrogate quantities employed. Meets required level 2."
